descriptionHtml:
this was a request by CrazyWolfGamer which i LOVED! and i think the saxons are just pure awesome. so this replaces all Whiterun Guards with Saxons still true to their original colors.

hope you like it and endorse if you do so i know my effort is well spent. and feel free to make requests as so far my 2 biggest requests have turned into ever evolving on-going projects, the \'Tartan Stormcloaks\' and the \'Crests Mod\'

Callaghan04
